This is a gap analysis for the following Dataset in SDE 64.

DRAINAGE¶

C. TREATED EFFLUENT NETWORK¶

This is an insight on the Feature classes attribute Completeness. The report highlight the Gaps existing in the dataset in the context of attributes having Null fields. it gives numerical quantity of each attribute field total null/un-filled fields as well as a graphical represention with other columns of a feature class.

Below are the feature classes existing in SDE.DRG_TREATED_EFFLUENT_NETWORK, whose gaps have been assessed.

   TSE Lagoon & Tanks
   TSE Scada Zone Boundary
   Treated Sewage Network Takamul Supply Zone Catchment Boundries
